title: Postponements and Cancellations on the Rise
description:
Wendi Nix, Todd McShay and David Pollack discuss this weekends cancellations and postponements, Notre Dame's potential, the comparison between Mac Jones and Kyle Trask, and the disappointing season starts for Michigan and Penn State.
